title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR file in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
OB: The out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time after exporting a directory and placing the exported JAR file in the same directory.
EB: The out of sync message is not displayed after overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time when the exported JAR file is not placed in the same directory as the exported directory (project).
SR: Ensure that the out of sync message is consistently displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time after exporting a directory and placing the exported JAR file in the same directory.
